{
  "stem": "19807.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I would come every afternoon, ride it all over, trot with it every day, until you could see-- we'd feel that he was getting bigger and bigger.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because he felt that by horses exercising all the time, it would give birth easier, which it did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I did not witness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wanted to witness it, but I didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But primarily-- but we were on tractors, we were in the fields, we were in the-- in the-- in anything that they had.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Citrus, they had citrus there, they would pack citruses, they would ship them out to the cities.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyplace-- there were so many different branches and every one of us would go and specialize in a different branch.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So like when we had the citrus, they went to the citrus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they went to the fruit branch, they went to the fruit branch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were also people that were just building, so I worked with them also in building, worked with some new construction there, whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but they were wonderful to us there, wonderful to the point that they wanted us to remain after our two years to become members of the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, I was one of those gung hos that says, you know, you taught us so well, we want to establish our own to show you that we're worthy of your tutelage.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we went and we founded our own, which the name of our kibbutz was called [INAUDIBLE], which means lights.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was in the Negev.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were the first 11 strategic points that the Jewish National Fund had the wisdom and the Ben-Gurion and all the officials at that time to establish because Ben-Gurion always felt that the Negev would be a big part of the developing of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
